{"tid":2258492,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"旅遊業界今早發起慢駛遊行，希望特區政府推出措施，切斷疫情，早日恢復通關。","createTime":"2020-10-26T05:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T06:19:27.000Z","uid":1249,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"461199a71a1b3a99acc84d87fa14ac7e968dcb3f","tid":2258492,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jfk4RGw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfk4RGw.jpg&h=08d2cc9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bea09tm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBea09tm.jpg&h=0f6f0bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有旅遊業界發起慢駛遊行，多輛大型旅遊巴早上在灣仔金紫荊廣場集合，沿途再有其他旅遊巴加入，其後慢駛至政府總部，希望特區政府推出措施，切斷疫情，早日恢復通關。<br />\n<br />\n香港旅行社東主協會會長葉慶寧表示，現時很多旅遊業界僱主都在「吃老本」，亦得悉不少旅遊業界打算在11月底的政府保就業計劃完結後，要求員工不要上班，形容現時情況嚴峻，希望政府盡快推行強制全民檢測，盡快切斷疫情，讓旅客往來。<br />\n<br />\n葉慶寧又指，本地遊反應未如預期理想，因為旅行社需要遵守程序和守則，加上本地遊市場不大，實際數字需再觀望多一兩個星期，但相信對整體旅遊業幫助不大，只是至少讓旅遊巴司機和導遊有些工作。<br />\n<br />\n參與遊行的旅遊業界又表示，希望政府盡快推出健康碼及關口快速測試，恢復香港通關，確保過關人流安全，令內地及澳門安心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556677-20201026.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556677-20201026.htm&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=02fa824b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556677-20201026.htm&h=60ba3fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556677-20201026.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c76dd05ed1651bcb23b15efd7d3be9b40b4ef75e","tid":2258492,"uid":52459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"香港毒瘤"},{"pid":"3b4b641e48bcff56a7aca754e88c3832342eb00e","tid":2258492,"uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c76dd05ed1651bcb23b15efd7d3be9b40b4ef75e","tid":2258492,"uid":52459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTi